      <paragraph>
        <num>(a)</num>
        <content>
          <p>The Business Population Estimates only provides a category for the public sector for businesses with zero or one employee. We have used the ratio of the private sector and applied it to the whole economy. Private sector businesses make up the vast majority of the business population, so aggregate results are not strongly affected by this.</p>
